cs.CR, cs.DC, cs.SE, cs.DB, cs.CY 

The paper discusses the characteristics and trade-offs of Distributed Ledger Technology (DLT), which is a topic related to computer security (cs.CR), distributed computing (cs.DC), software engineering (cs.SE), databases (cs.DB), and cryptography (cs.CY). However, since the paper focuses more on the technical aspects of DLT and its design decisions, cs.CR and cs.DC are the most likely categories.
